# phase-flow v2 guardrails (static fallback)

This rule mirrors critical guardrails when hook injection is unreliable. Fail-closed enforcement lives in
the `beforeSubmitPrompt` hook (`before-submit-guardrails.py`).

- Route memory ops through `memory-preflight` / `providers/<memory.provider>.md` — never call Recallium directly.
- Never store raw transcripts or secrets in memory.
- CI readiness: run `scripts/check-gate.sh` — never hand-roll a green verdict.
- `sw-` commands only for this plugin's workflow surface.
